                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Uncertainties are one sigma of the",
                "measured values. Error propagation for the weighting",
                "factors for the calculation of mean cross sections",
                "and proton intensities essentially entailed the",
                "reflection of radioactivity counting statistics.",
                "Contributions from uncertainties associated with the",
                "monitor cross sections, spectrometer efficiency",
                "calibration, photon intensities, etc. were not",
                "included, so that the listed errors are but minimum",
                "values for these experiments."
              ]
